    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "Twelve of thirteen V&V 40 credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels. The single gap (Test conditions, achieved Gradation 2 vs. required Gradation 3) is offset by the high relevance of the validation activity to the COU, the tight quantitative agreement across all three QoIs (E/uval < 1.96, all differences < 10%), and the medium model risk level. The overall credibility profile is sufficient to support the regulatory decision for this Class II device.",
